snippet.title: Songs Of Conquest – Console Release Date Announcement XBOX PS5
snippet.description: The time is finally here! On November 12th Songs of Conquest releases on Consoles.  Wield magic,  lead mighty armies and defeat your enemies, Now from the comfort of your couch!
